<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182117>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 20. Tautoneura longiprocessa n. sp. 11. Head and thorax, dorsal view. 12. Pygofer lobe, lateral view. 13. Subgenital plate. 14. Aedeagus, ventral view. 15. Aedeagus, lateral view. 16. Style. 17. Connective. 18. Abdominal apodemes. 19. Forewing. 20. Hindwing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/182117/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182118>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21 – 39. Tautoneura arachisi (Matsumura, 1916): 21. Aedeagus, ventral view. 22. Aedeagus, lateral view; Tautoneura choui Ma, 1983: 23. Aedeagus, ventral view. 24. Aedeagus, lateral view; T. formosa (Dworakowska, 1970): 25. Aedeagus, ventral view. 26. Aedeagus, lateral view; T. fusca (Dworakowska, 1970): 27. Style. 28. Aedeagus, ventral view. 29. Aedeagus, lateral view; T. mori (Matsumura, 1906): 30. Head and thorax, dorsal view. 31. Aedeagus, lateral view; T. prima Dworakowska, 1979: 32. Aedeagus, ventral view. 33. Aedeagus, lateral view; T. sinica (Dworakowska, 1970): 34. Style. 35. Aedeagus, ventral view. 36. Aedeagus, lateral view; T. tripunctula (Melicher, 1903): 37. Aedeagus, ventral view. 38. Aedeagus, lateral view. 39. Forewing. (Note: Fig. 30 after Kuoh, others after Dworakowska)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/182118/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

